{"tid":1870792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兒登仔係咪次次都俾五毛狗帶風向先安樂 呢兩日咁多明顯五毛出黎叫唔好理李文亮係咪仲唔知咩事","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T09:00:38.000Z","uid":288670,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76867d10dc9ceaa526ef766717cc9da5eae96f07","tid":1870792,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母一個post 都已經搵到三隻殭屍五毛 口徑仲要好相似 <br />\n<br />\n依家仲有一班帶風向既開post 將手足叫人去輸出革命 搞亂支那屈成係建設民主支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/Uploads/20200207/5e3c73c6a05d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2FUploads%2F20200207%2F5e3c73c6a05d7.png&h=9648b01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDAzODA2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDAzODA2&h=ced0fcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDAzODA3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDAzODA3&h=766c9b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDAzODA4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDAzODA4&h=ebbba322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDAzODA5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDAzODA5&h=5307c447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDAzODEw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDAzODEw&h=979af231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＃我要言论自由（支爆來了）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866465\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n而另一個post 又搵到兩隻 其中一隻仲要係出名五毛回憶小子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDA0MDc1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDA0MDc1&h=48a6e078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.userver.net/?MDA0MDc2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.userver.net%2F%3FMDA0MDc2&h=5a134f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbYXAWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbYXAWQ.png&h=b0a85a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家班巴打係要食李文亮呢個血饅頭 搞亂支那 唔撚係要幫支那建設民主支那呀屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n搞到支那人鬼打鬼 死既係佢地 就算失敗香港人都無損失<br />\n<br />\n你班兒登仔訓撚醒未 次次俾五毛撚 好撚過癮？"},{"pid":"8a326ce490dc8f300441b779579d86691636d6fe","tid":1870792,"uid":96148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"兒登仔點解咁易被人帶風向？<br />\n因為好多都好撚蠢，一味情緒主導<br />\n見之前醫護罷工，成個熱門得邊度有得買口罩的post就知，成日話支那人停留喺口腔期，兒登仔咪一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之食訓玩痾性、生活必需、情緒主導標題黨post就上到熱門<br />\n到後期醫護停罷，輕易就被五毛分化左去屌9醫護，屌佢地無堅持，笑撚死我<br />\n有五毛狗就預左，但咁易被人帶風向就真係抵撚死"},{"pid":"d7644b6733f41a7874ef414e2a1c4a9e06650d7d","tid":1870792,"uid":288670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a326ce490dc8f300441b779579d86691636d6fe","tid":1870792,"uid":96148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"兒登仔點解咁易被人帶風向？<br />\n因為好多都好撚蠢，一味情緒主導<br />\n見之前醫護罷工，成個熱門得邊度有得買口罩的post就知，成日話支那人停留喺口腔期，兒登仔咪一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之食訓玩痾性、生活必需、情緒主導標題黨post就上到熱門<br />\n到後期醫護停罷，輕易就被五毛分化左去屌9醫護，屌佢地無堅持，笑撚死我<br />\n有五毛狗就預左，但咁易被人帶風向就真係抵撚死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"仲要成日講獨立 不過眼見個咁好搞亂支那既機會都唔撚去利用 少少政治手段都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗真係班人智有缺陷先會咁"},{"pid":"c249cd1ea6412696c2b76d44d5ca4c3e5dcd7f76","tid":1870792,"uid":96148